Easy Tax Application (1.0.0)

Download OpenAPI specification:Download

Pixfar developer team: pixfar@gmail.com URL: https://pixfar.com

Introducing our user-friendly Easy Tax REST API, designed to simplify tax-related data integration. With our intuitive platform, preparing and submitting your taxes has never been easier. Say goodbye to complicated forms and confusing jargon; our application guides you through each step with clear, plain-language instructions.
